<L>__{exterior thatched hut later day}
<A>__{a pile of bodies lie by the steps in the pouring rain. the bodies are both south vietnamese and american. their heads are all variously blown to pieces and several huge rats are already feeding on them.}
<L>__{interior thatched hut table area day}
<A>__{nick is at the table now, opposite a south vietnamese. he holds the pistol by his chin, spins the cylinder. his face is twitching, dripping sweat and both he and his opponent are holding onto each other's eyes as if they had been at it for a long time. nick raises the pistol to his temple, clicks out. the guards murmur. nick pushes the pistol across the table.}
